They dissipated.

00:36:42.670 --> 00:36:44.843
So it doesn't always happen.

00:36:44.843 --> 00:36:45.760
Doesn't always happen.

00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:48.010
Andrew?

00:36:48.010 --> 00:36:51.340
AUDIENCE: Just as-- it
