00:37:23.710 --> 00:37:25.810
mass strikes.

00:37:25.810 --> 00:37:28.870
You can call it-- you
call a general strike.

00:37:28.870 --> 00:37:31.420
And if the general
strike is effective,

00:37:31.420 --> 00:37:34.305
