00:41:05.640 --> 00:41:09.870
Social movements
work by demonstrating

00:41:09.870 --> 00:41:14.070
that it matters
to enough people,

00:41:14.070 --> 00:41:16.050
that you have to
take it into account.

00:41:16.050 --> 00:41:19.290
And if the policymaker
knows that it

00:41:19.290 --> 00:41:21.510
